569. 员工薪水中位数 Hard

# 一言难尽

570. 至少有5名直接下属的经理 Medium

SELECT Name
FROM Employee LEFT JOIN
(SELECT ManagerId, COUNT(ManagerId) num
FROM Employee e1
GROUP BY ManagerId) t1 
ON Employee.Id = t1.ManagerId
WHERE t1.num >= 5

# 先构造满足条件的表然后联结得出结果

